a mutually exclusive manner.

605
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,560
In gliomas,

606
00:34:06,560 --> 00:34:07,840
mutations in IDH

607
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:08,920
have what kind of effect

608
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,040
