615
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,480
and secondary high-grade tumors.

616
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:20,400
It is associated with
improved patient survival.

617
00:34:29,240 --> 00:34:30,040
Very good.

618
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:35,240
Miss Su, your answer is perfect.

619
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:36,880
However, given that you arrived late,

620
00:34:37,240 --> 00:34:39,280
