It's good that you dislike him.

702
00:38:26,100 --> 00:38:27,420
I was worried that you still loved him,

703
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:28,620
but now I feel relieved.

704
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:29,860
Let me tell you,

705
00:38:29,860 --> 00:38:31,660
I heard that Li Wantong

706
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:33,300
has already made her move

707
00:38:33,420 --> 00:38:34,700
and gotten together with Dr. Gu.

708
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,460
Now she's his official girlfriend.

709
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:39,700
Don't worry.

710
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:42,060
Dr. Gu has gotten over you already.

711
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:43,900
He doesn't want
to be your boyfriend now.

712
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:45,100
He just wants to be your boss.

713
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:47,100
Just think of him

714
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,500
as a walking money bag,

715
00:38:48,580 --> 00:38:50,060
drain him dry, and be done with it.

716
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:52,060
Su Wei'an,

717
00:38:52,060 --> 00:38:53,100
with you hem and haw like this,

718
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:54,620
I suspect you still have feelings
for Dr. Gu!

719
00:38:54,620 --> 00:38:55,620
Not at all!

720
00:38:59,220 --> 00:39:00,220
Never mind.

721
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:01,700
It's just a job.

722
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:04,000
There's no medical translation
Su Wei'an can't do!

723
00:39:04,180 --> 00:39:05,260
That's the spirit!

724
00:39:05,620 --> 00:39:06,420
Come on!

725
00:39:07,420 --> 00:39:08,620
I spent a whole day

726
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:10,220
